Open source platforms specifically created to help open and/or co-operative projects include: 

#[[Goteo]] for crowdfunding the commons; Open Funding and Bountysource for cofunding free software; 
#[[Gittip]] for giving small weekly cash gifts to people you love and are inspired by; 
#Snowdrift, a monthly matched patronage system; and 
#Coopfunding.net, a wordpress powered crowdfunding platform for co-ops in Spain


